`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Call_Lightning
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast 'call lightning'

 This spell works only out of doors, and only when the weather is bad. It calls
down lightning bolts that strike everything in the immediate area that isn't
you.  As this is an area attack, use care when casting because everything you
hit will attack in return.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
